## 🔑 The Claude Prompting Formula (That Actually Works)

### 🧠 Reusable Base Template

<role>Define who Claude is (expert role)</role>

<task>Define exactly what needs to be produced</task>

<context>
Provide all available input:
- Documents
- Emails
- Tables
- Transcripts
- Constraints
</context>

<rules>
- What Claude must do
- What Claude must NOT do
- Quality criteria
- Limits (length, tone, format)
- Do not invent information
</rules>

<output>Describe the exact final format</output>

💡 **Pro tip:** You don’t need to use **all tags every time**.  
Use what applies — but **more structure = higher accuracy**.

